lead_paragraph: Jake Arrieta's bid to become the second pitcher to throw consecutive no-hitters has ended with a broken-bat single on his fifth pitch.

headline.print_headline: Arrieta's Bid for 2nd Straight No-Hitter Ends on 5th Pitch
